---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 298
  - Description: hutdîth qudsî
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Just Proportioning of
    Ritual
By: Muhammad
---
If a man is so occupied with recollecting Me that he forgets to pray
to Me, I grant him a nobler gift than that which I accord to those who
petition Me.
